{"id": "1488481880109220000", "channel_id": "1488481880109220000", "type": 0, "author_id": "353194690025357314", "author_name": "blumenwiz", "author_bot": false, "content": "The biggest reason I quit gacha games is if they don't respect my time and the daily/weekly grind becomes too annoying. Using auto battle alleviates a long term burnout and makes the game fun because I get to decide when I want to spent time on the game.\nUsing auto battle in D-Zone already comes with a big punishment: Instead of a 400 Alert 5 clear I will only do a 350 Alert 3 clear. That is a fair trade off. I don't have time nor the motivation to go for a high score in D-Zone every time. In fact I have lost interest in D-Zone as of late and am more interested in Story Mode and collecting/building more units. The removal of auto battle from D-Zone and Character Trials have made my experience with this game worse and the changes feel completely unnecessary", "timestamp": "2026-03-31T10:15:34.874000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🙂‍↕️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1488481880109220000", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Enable Auto Battle for D-Zone/Tide and Character Trials again", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
